## 🏫 Course Information

### Getting Help
- **Office Hours:** Check course schedule
- **Discussion Forum:** Post questions and help classmates
- **Email:** Contact instructor for assistance

### Prerequisites
- Basic programming knowledge
- Understanding of variables, functions, and control structures
- Familiarity with command line/terminal

### Learning Resources
- Work through [tutorials](tutorials/)
- Complete [assignments](assignments/) on time
- Practice with [code examples](code-examples/)
- Solve [practice problems](practice-problems/) regularly

